VWH-Platform-Info version 0.01
==============================

Platform information module. This module is used to abstract out the differences
between OpenVZ and Vkern when obtaining platform specific information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

OpenVZ on Linux and Vkern on FreeBSD. 

